msgid ""
"Inventory Klein for Ray dependencies on Ray private APIs and Developer APIs."
msgstr "梳理 Klein for Ray 对 Ray 私有 API 和 Developer API 的依赖。"

msgid "Ray private-API inventory"
msgstr "Ray 私有 API 清单"

msgid ""
"The shipped `ray.klein` package has no direct imports from `ray._private`, "
"`ray.data._internal`, or `ray.air`. Bounded representations, batched column "
"validation and ragged arrays are implemented locally."
msgstr "发布的 `ray.klein` 包不直接从 `ray._private`、`ray.data._internal` 或 `ray.air` 导入。有限数据表示、分批列校验和不规则数组均在本地实现。"

msgid ""
"The project still uses several Ray Data extension classes whose stability is "
"DeveloperAPI rather than PublicAPI, including datasource and datasink base "
"classes. That is why the initial release intentionally supports only the Ray "
"2.56 minor line. Widening the range requires unit, integration, and clean-"
"wheel tests against the proposed Ray version."
msgstr "项目仍使用若干稳定性级别为 DeveloperAPI 而非 PublicAPI 的 Ray Data 扩展类，包括 datasource 和 datasink 基类。这正是首个版本有意仅支持 Ray 2.56 次版本系列的原因。扩展范围前，必须在拟支持的 Ray 版本上运行单元测试、集成测试和干净 wheel 测试。"

msgid ""
"CI rejects direct private imports. Code that requires a private Ray API is "
"not accepted into the package."
msgstr "CI 会拒绝直接导入私有 API。需要 Ray 私有 API 的代码不会被纳入该包。"

msgid "CI rejects unlisted private imports and private imports outside `_compat`. Widening the Ray version range requires verifying every symbol above and adding minimum/maximum-version clean-wheel tests. The preferred migration is always to delete an inventory item when Ray exposes a public replacement."
msgstr "CI 会拒绝未列入清单的私有导入，以及 `_compat` 之外的私有导入。扩大 Ray 版本范围时，必须验证上述每个符号，并增加最低和最高版本的干净 wheel 测试。当 Ray 提供公共替代项时，首选迁移方式始终是删除对应的清单条目。"

msgid "Ray Data 2.56 does not expose public equivalents for evaluating one expression against an externally supplied Arrow block or for applying its datasource filesystem retry wrapper. `ray.klein._compat.ray_data_expression` therefore adapts these symbols:"
msgstr "Ray Data 2.56 尚未提供公共等价 API，无法针对外部传入的 Arrow 块求值单个表达式，也无法应用其数据源文件系统重试包装器。因此，`ray.klein._compat.ray_data_expression` 会适配以下符号："

msgid "The adapter owns task-context construction, class-UDF initialization, single-block evaluation, URI resolution, and retry setup. Callers use only the stable Klein adapter surface."
msgstr "该适配器负责构造任务上下文、初始化类 UDF、执行单块求值、解析 URI 和设置重试。调用方只使用稳定的 Klein 适配器接口。"

msgid "The shipped `ray.klein` package isolates every private Ray dependency in `ray.klein._compat`. Normal API, runtime, state, connector, and SQL modules may not import private Ray symbols. CI scans the real package tree and compares the imports against this exact inventory, so a missing source directory cannot silently turn the guard green."
msgstr "发布的 `ray.klein` 包将所有 Ray 私有依赖隔离在 `ray.klein._compat` 中。普通 API、运行时、状态、连接器和 SQL 模块不得导入 Ray 私有符号。CI 会扫描真实的包目录树，并将导入与这份精确清单比较，因此源目录缺失时不可能悄悄让门禁通过。"

msgid "`ray.data._internal.execution.interfaces.task_context.TaskContext`;"
msgstr "`ray.data._internal.execution.interfaces.task_context.TaskContext`；"

msgid "`ray.data._internal.planner.plan_expression.expression_evaluator.eval_expr`;"
msgstr "`ray.data._internal.planner.plan_expression.expression_evaluator.eval_expr`；"

msgid "`ray.data._internal.planner.plan_expression.expression_visitors._CallableClassUDFCollector`;"
msgstr "`ray.data._internal.planner.plan_expression.expression_visitors._CallableClassUDFCollector`；"

msgid "`ray.data._internal.util.RetryingPyFileSystem`;"
msgstr "`ray.data._internal.util.RetryingPyFileSystem`；"

msgid "`ray.data.datasource.path_util._resolve_paths_and_filesystem`;"
msgstr "`ray.data.datasource.path_util._resolve_paths_and_filesystem`；"

msgid "`ray.data.datasource.path_util._validate_and_wrap_filesystem`."
msgstr "`ray.data.datasource.path_util._validate_and_wrap_filesystem`。"
